org.apache.commons.pool2

接口 TrackedUse


  • public interface TrackedUse
    This interface allows pooled objects to make information available about when and how they were used available to the object pool. The object pool may, but is not required, to use this information to make more informed decisions when determining the state of a pooled object - for instance whether or not the object has been abandoned.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0
